OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine and dry day to come with
OL,6,Fplenty of sunshine. The sunshine may
OL,7,Fturn a little hazy throughout the
OL,8,Fafternoon, but despite this it will be
OL,9,Ffeeling very warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRemaining fine and dry this
OL,12,Fevening, before cloud increases
OL,13,Ftowards midnight. Overnight some spots
OL,14,Fof rain are possible but most
OL,15,Fremaining dry. A mild night for many.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FAny early cloud quickly
OL,18,Fbreaking up giving way to a dry and
OL,19,Fsunny day, although sunshine maybe a
OL,20,Flittle hazy at times. Feeling very
OL,21,Fwarm in the strong sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
