OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FRemaining dry and settled throughout
OL,7,FSunday and early next week with plenty
OL,8,Fof sunshine. Feeling hot by day with
OL,9,Fpotentially some warm nights too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
